imdb.plot outline: Reel NW features independent films from and about the Pacific Northwest. Each year, we strive to bring you unique stories by diverse filmmakers from across our region and this year, more than half of the films are made by women. From thought-provoking feature documentaries to narrative shorts and student films, Reel NW showcases our region's talents, stunning environment and the issues that affect us.
